data.description: Welcome to your dream home near Lake Belton and Belton High School in Belton Texas! This exquisite 4 bedroom, 2 bath house combines modern comfort with a prime location, offering you the best of both worlds. Convenience is key, and this property delivers. Located in close proximity to Belton High School, you'll appreciate the ease of commuting for both students and parents alike. The surrounding area offers a wealth of amenities, including shopping centers, restaurants, and parks. PCS-ing to Fort Cavazos? This home is approximately 28 minutes away! Schedule your private tour with your local REALTOR today and make this dream home your reality!
